helpTextPostfix.value:
To have a great conversation, ask me questions as if I was a real programmer:

* **Show me the code** you want to talk about by having the files open and selecting the most important lines.
* **Make refinements** by asking me follow-up questions, adding clarifications, providing errors, etc.
* **Review my suggested code** and tell me about issues or improvements, so I can iterate on it.

You can also ask me questions about your editor selection by [starting an inline chat session](command:inlineChat.start).

Learn more about [GitHub Copilot](https://docs.github.com/copilot/using-github-copilot/getting-started-with-github-copilot?tool=vscode&utm_source=editor&utm_medium=chat-panel&utm_campaign=2024q3-em-MSFT-getstarted) in [Visual Studio Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/overview).

response.value:
Snippet with error: `<nav>`
Location of error: "Navigation Bar"
WCAG Guideline violated: 2.4.1 Bypass Blocks
Detection Algorithm: Check if there are mechanisms to bypass blocks of content that are repeated on multiple web pages.
Explanation of Error: There are no skip links provided. Skip links allow users to skip over repetitive content like navigation links.

Snippet with error: `<video autoplay>`
Location of error: Inside the "Video Section"
WCAG Guideline violated: 1.4.2 Audio Control
Detection Algorithm: Check if audio that plays automatically for more than 3 seconds has a control mechanism.
Explanation of Error: The video element is set to autoplay, but there is no control provided to turn off the sound.

Snippet with error: `<button class="play-btn"></button>`
Location of error: Inside the "Browse Music Section"
WCAG Guideline violated: 2.1.1 Keyboard
Detection Algorithm: Check if all functionality is operable through a keyboard interface.
Explanation of Error: The play button doesn't have a discernible name, which can make it difficult for keyboard users to understand its function.

Snippet with error: `<form>`
Location of error: Inside the "Create Playlist Section"
WCAG Guideline violated: 3.3.4 Error Prevention (Legal, Financial, Data)
Detection Algorithm: Check if forms that cause legal commitments or financial transactions, modify or delete user-controllable data, or submit test responses have at least one of the following: Reversible, Checked, Confirmed.
Explanation of Error: The form doesn't have any error prevention mechanisms in place. While this form may not cause legal or financial transactions, it's still a good practice to provide error prevention for forms that modify user-controllable data.

Snippet with error: `<video autoplay>`
Location of error: Inside the "Video Section"
WCAG Guideline violated: 2.2.2 Pause, Stop, Hide
Detection Algorithm: Check if moving, blinking, scrolling, or auto-updating information can be paused, stopped, or hidden by the user.
Explanation of Error: The video element is set to autoplay without providing controls to pause, stop, or hide the video.
